profile_positions.description:
Supporting Sustainable Business-Society interfaces by working with:

- Companies and entrepreneurs on improving the sustainability of their supply chains, new business models, product development, strategic stakeholder engagement and the business relevance of social & ecological impact;
- Universities on cross-fertilization of scientific and practical knowledge;
- Governmental and non-governmental organizations on public private partnerships that generate shared value for shared goals with shared approaches. 

We worked with: DSM, Adecco, Cordaid, the University of Amsterdam, the Dutch ministry of foreign affairs, TMG, Rotterdam & Groningen municipality, the Royal Tropical Institute (KIT), Consumers International, Enviu and others

Merged with the Rock Group in 2014
